      <div class='l'>
      <label >(A7)</label>
      </div>
    </div></div><div class='html-p'>Next, we evaluate the integrals (<a href="#FD34-jimaging-11-00014" class="html-disp-formula">A7</a>) by calculus. By using the transformation
        <div class='html-disp-formula-info' id=''>
