      </div>
      <div class='l'>
      <label >(A9)</label>
      </div>
    </div>From (<a href="#FD33-jimaging-11-00014" class="html-disp-formula">A6</a>) and (<a href="#FD35-jimaging-11-00014" class="html-disp-formula">A8</a>), the interior equations are obtained,
        <div class='html-disp-formula-info' id=''>
      <div class='f'>
        <math display='block'><semantics>
  <mtable displaystyle="true">
    <mtr>
      <mtd/>
      <mtd/>
